articles.author: MICHAEL LIEDTKE
articles.title: Will the antitrust showdown launched under Biden turn into 'Let's Make A Deal' under Trump? - The Associated Press
articles.description: The U.S. antitrust watchdogs that pounced on Big Tech and deterred dealmaking throughout corporate America during President Joe Biden’s administration may be tamer and kept on a shorter leash by President-elect Donald Trump after he returns to the White House…
